events.name: Live Sports Screening
events.description:
Welcome to Korma Sutra - a vibrant shisha venue that offers a unique fusion of relaxation and exhilaration. Step into our inviting space, adorned with plush seating and ambient lighting, where guests gather to indulge in the art of shisha while catching the latest sporting events on our large screens. Whether you're a devoted fan cheering for your favorite team or simply seeking a laid-back atmosphere to unwind with friends, our venue provides the perfect setting. 

With a diverse selection of premium shisha flavors and an extensive menu of refreshments, every visit promises a memorable experience. Join us for an unforgettable blend of leisure and entertainment.
